entry.value: select distinct pd from ProcessRun pr join pr.proDefinition pd where pr.runStatus=? order by pd.defId desc
select distinct vo from ProcessRun as vo join vo.processForms as pf where pf.creatorId=? order by vo.createtime desc
select distinct vo from ProcessRun as vo join vo.processForms as pf where pf.creatorId=? and vo.runStatus=? order by vo.createtime desc
select vo from OutMailUserSeting vo right join vo.appUser au where au.delFlag=0
select vo from Regulation vo where vo.status = ? and (vo.recDepIds like ? or vo.recUserIds like ? )
